CBRE is pleased to offer 15 Dalton Road, Thomastown, available for sale via Public Deadline Sale closing Wednesday 30th May 2018 at 3.00PM AEST (unless sold prior).

15 Dalton Road is located approximately 13km from Melbourne's CBD and 22km* from the Melbourne Airport. The property enjoys ease of access to major arterials such as the Metropolitan Ring Road, Hume Freeway and Sydney Road.

Dalton Road is considered a premier location as it is situated within a popular commercial precinct and enjoys ample exposure to passing traffic. Neighbouring Bunnings, this property is also within close proximity to the Thomastown large format retail precinct including Harvey Norman, The Good Guys, Baby Bunting, Petbarn and JB Hi-Fi.

The vacant land parcel provides the following key features:
+ Site area: 14,920sqm*
+ Two significant street frontages (Dalton Road & Dunstans Court)
+ Potential for service station/car wash/industrial/large format retail (STCA)
+ Rare opportunity in Industrial 1 Zone
+ Permit approved for service station comprising five bowsers facing Dalton Road, ancillary retail store plus 10 unit office/warehouse development

For further information regarding this opportunity or to arrange an inspection, kindly contact CBRE.
